## API Usage (Local)

Ollama exposes a local REST API at `http://localhost:11434`:

```bash
# Chat via curl
curl http://localhost:11434/api/chat -d '{
  "model": "llama3.1:8b",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Hello, what can you do?" }
  ],
  "stream": false
}'
```

Compatible with the **OpenAI API format** — works with tools like Open WebUI, Continue.dev, and most AI clients.

